816
01:17:52,005 --> 01:17:54,674
The Old Man is still
holding your marker!

817
01:17:55,592 --> 01:17:59,638
Matt! Matt!

818
01:17:59,679 --> 01:18:01,223
I'm gonna kill
that motherfucker.

819
01:18:01,848 --> 01:18:03,308
