fill, and he might well come after us.

824
01:18:13,318 --> 01:18:14,402
He's never gonna
come after us.

825
01:18:14,486 --> 01:18:15,654
How the fuck do you know?

826
01:18:15,695 --> 01:18:18,198
Blue, he's a sick,
compulsive gambler.

827
01:18:18,281 --> 01:18:19,741
You know what he thrives on?
The action, that's it.

828
01:18:19,824 --> 01:18:21,534
We got him right
where we want him.

829
01:18:21,576 --> 01:18:24,370
He's going to come to us
with his hat in his hand.

830
01:18:24,412 --> 01:18:25,914
You understand?

831
01:18:25,997 --> 01:18:28,333
He's either going to end up
in prison, insanity or death.

832
01:18:33,046 --> 01:18:35,840
Double Johnnie Walker on the
rocks. I'll be over there.

833
01:18:51,522 --> 01:18:52,982
Thank you.

834
01:19:00,865 --> 01:19:02,283
Fuck that Old Man.

835
01:19:10,666 --> 01:19:13,336
