or from them?

846
01:20:02,384 --> 01:20:05,220
That was from me,
because I wanted to.

847
01:20:07,806 --> 01:20:09,433
Because you felt sorry for me.

848
01:20:11,643 --> 01:20:13,270
Because I wanted you.

849
01:20:16,190 --> 01:20:17,733
You did that real good.

850
01:20:27,451 --> 01:20:32,372
Besides you, the Old Man and Blue, you
know if there's anybody else involved?

851
01:20:33,624 --> 01:20:36,209
I have no idea.

852
01:20:36,251 --> 01:20:40,130
Could be just us, could be
hundreds of others just like us.

853
01:20:41,882 --> 01:20:43,634
I don't wanna know.
You're smart.

854
01:20:45,427 --> 01:20:50,307
It's just like
these folks, man,

855
01:20:50,390 --> 01:20:54,061
they might tell you to kill your
mama, your brother, your sister.

856
01:20:55,979 --> 01:20:59,816
Your child's step-daddy,
you know.

857
01:21:01,568 --> 01:21:03,403
And it don't work for me.

858
01:21:03,445 --> 01:21:09,993
You survived that. You
walked away. Walk away again.

859
01:21:10,076 --> 01:21:12,913
I ain't running no more.
Tired of running.

860
01:21:20,670 --> 01:21:22,797
(BELLS TOLLING)

861
01:21:43,651 --> 01:21:45,320
Matt?

862
01:22:00,668 --> 01:22:02,128
Matt?

863
01:22:02,170 --> 01:22:03,671
PRIEST: The Lord is my
shepherd, I shall not want...

864
01:22:05,006 --> 01:22:06,007
Matt?

865
01:22:14,515 --> 01:22:17,852
He leadeth me beside the
still waters. He restoreth...

866
01:22:30,615 --> 01:22:31,574
Matt?

867
01:22:39,790 --> 01:22:41,876
He restoreth my soul...

868
01:22:49,341 --> 01:22:53,220
He leadeth me in the paths of
righteousness for his name's sake.

869
01:22:55,764 --> 01:22:58,767
Yea, though I walk through the
valley of the shadow of death...

870
01:22:58,809 --> 01:23:02,646
STEVE: You guys know why we're
here, and you know what's at stake.

871
01:23:02,730 --> 01:23:04,023
Where's Wheeler?

872
01:23:04,106 --> 01:23:06,734
He's got a special assignment,
don't worry about it.

873
01:23:06,775 --> 01:23:09,528
All right, fan out,
and watch my back.

874
01:24:16,052 --> 01:24:17,178
What are you doing here?

875
01:24:17,262 --> 01:24:19,264
I came to pay my respects.

876
01:24:19,347 --> 01:24:21,266
You didn't have to
wait for me.

877
01:24:22,392 --> 01:24:24,686
I see you brought
the long rifle.

878
01:24:24,728 --> 01:24:25,687
You know it.

879
01:24:25,729 --> 01:24:28,940
I've already done my recon.

880
01:24:29,024 --> 01:24:33,695
Higher ground, on top of that mausoleum
looks like the best spot right there.

881
01:24:35,613 --> 01:24:37,866
It's exactly
what I was thinking.

882
01:25:08,771 --> 01:25:12,275
How'd you know it was me?
Why didn't you kill Blue?

883
01:25:16,154 --> 01:25:18,739
See, unfortunately, Tim
Wheeler knew my sad story

884
01:25:18,781 --> 01:25:21,159
about how I passed out
in my flophouse.

885
01:25:21,242 --> 01:25:24,871
