a guilty conscience.

889
01:25:40,761 --> 01:25:42,763
He was going to crack,
I didn't have a choice.

890
01:25:42,805 --> 01:25:46,142
No, I think you did
have a choice.

891
01:25:46,225 --> 01:25:50,813
I don't think you had to steal the money
and I don't think you had to kill my partner,

892
01:25:50,896 --> 01:25:52,148
but you're just
a piece of shit, Steve.

893
01:25:54,275 --> 01:25:56,819
