910
01:27:01,258 --> 01:27:04,761
If you ever want to see Becky
again, then lower your gun.

911
01:27:51,891 --> 01:27:53,601
Go get them!
All right! Let's go!

912
01:27:58,189 --> 01:28:01,067
God damn it, get up, get up!
You're not dead.

913
01:28:01,150 --> 01:28:03,528
