939
01:34:36,083 --> 01:34:37,668
German shepherd.

940
01:34:37,752 --> 01:34:41,464
Really?
Yeah. I told you before.

941
01:34:41,547 --> 01:34:43,007
Please. How many times
have you told me before?

942
01:34:43,090 --> 01:34:45,635
